# Flutter/Dart/Pub related
**/doc/api/
**/ios/Flutter/.last_build_id
.dart_tool/
.flutter-plugins
.flutter-plugins-dependencies
.packages
.pub-cache/
.pub/

# NOTE: /build/ is intentionally NOT ignored in this repo. Normally Flutter
# projects exclude it as regenerable output, but here we ship the
# pre-compiled build/web/ so the Dockerfile can COPY it directly without
# needing a Flutter SDK at build time. Other build/ subdirs (desktop,
# mobile) aren't used by the Docker image, so ignore them specifically:
/build/linux/
/build/macos/
/build/windows/
/build/ios/
/build/android/

# Node modules for the web JS bundle — regenerable with `yarn install`.
web/js/node_modules/
build/web/js/node_modules/

